# River generator
Here is a basic example of MarkovJunior used to procedurally generate rivers.

Load the library first:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
PacletDirectoryLoad[
  NotebookDirectory[]//ParentDirectory
];
Needs["CoffeeLiqueur`Workshop`MarkovJunior`"->"m`"];

